result.name: morecambe-bay-map-of-zostera-beds
result.notes: This map shows the area covered by seagrass beds in the west part of Morecambe Bay, near Walney Island. The data were obtained by the MESH Project as the results of a data collation contract undertaken by OSPAR.
result.title: Morecambe Bay map of Zostera beds
